      "instruction": "<p>Once the gnocchi and Fable pulled mushrooms are almost done, mix your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and<strong> cornflour </strong>in a jug</p><p>Add 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[550ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> soft cheese </strong>and<strong> cracked black pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>cacio e pepe sauce</strong></p>",
